There are some layout differences between the adapters pictured in the FCC entries for TE7T1U and TE7T1UV1. * "2052500513" is silkscreened on the board in the FCC photos for TE7T1U. * "2052500564" is silkscreened on the board in the FCC photos for TE7T1UV1.
